msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/date"
msgid "June 10th-16th, 1944 · Hill 192, Normandy, France "
msgstr "10-16 de junio, 1944 - Colina 192, Normandía, Francia "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/doctrine_allround"
msgid "Doctrine: All-Round"
msgstr "Doctrina: Completa"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/doctrine_defensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Defensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Defensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/doctrine_irregular"
msgid "Doctrine: Irregular"
msgstr "Doctrina: Irregular"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/doctrine_offensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Offensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Ofensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/hq"
msgid "Warnings issued about US troops close to HQ:%1%/3"
msgstr ""
"Advertencias sobre tropas estadounidenses cerca del cuartel general:%1%/3"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/lose_hq"
msgid ""
"The enemy entered the HQ and you failed to have them eliminated after three "
"warnings."
msgstr ""
"El enemigo ha entrado en el Cuartel General y no has conseguido eliminarlo "
"después de tres avisos."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/name"
msgid "The Hills of Saint-Lô"
msgstr "Las colinas de Saint-Lô"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/name_big"
msgid "The Hills of Saint-Lô"
msgstr "Las colinas de Saint-Lô"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Fallschirmjäger! We are deployed here to assist the 352nd Infantry Division "
"in holding the Americans back! We are severely outgunned, but well "
"entrenched."
msgstr ""
"¡Fallschirmjäger! ¡Estamos desplegados aquí para ayudar a la 352 División de "
"Infantería a contener a los americanos! Nos vemos severamente superados en "
"número, pero estamos bien atrincherados."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"We will defend this position until the rest of our motorised Kampfgruppe "
"arrives."
msgstr ""
"Defenderemos esta posición hasta que llegue el resto de nuestro Kampfgruppe "
"motorizado."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"Spread out, man the guns and mortars, and lay down obstacles to reinforce "
"our defensive line!"
msgstr ""
"¡Dispersaos, preparad los cañones y morteros, y estableced barricadas para "
"reforzar nuestra línea defensiva!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"The enemy is expected to come from the northern slopes. We need to use the "
"terrain to our advantage!"
msgstr ""
"Se espera que el enemigo venga desde las laderas del norte. ¡Tenemos que "
"utilizar el terreno a nuestro favor!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/05"
msgid ""
"The hedgerows make it hard for us to see the enemy approaching, but equally "
"allow us to channel the enemy into kill zones."
msgstr ""
"Los setos nos dificultarán ver al enemigo acercarse, pero por otra parte nos "
"serán útiles para dirigir al enemigo a su muerte."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/06"
msgid ""
"The enemy has dug out positions on the northern slope, stand your ground and "
"get ready to harrass the enemy on the corner of every hedgerow!"
msgstr ""
"El enemigo ha cavado posiciones en la ladera norte, ¡mantened posiciones y "
"preparaos para hostigar al enemigo en cada giro y en cada arbusto!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"These first enemy squads are probably the scouts. Get ready for some serious "
"attacks!"
msgstr ""
"Estos primeros escuadrones enemigos probablemente sean los exploradores. "
"¡Prepárate para el ataque!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"The enemy artillery ceased fire. I suspect they will use spotters to "
"pinpoint some of our specific positions for bombardment."
msgstr ""
"La artillería enemiga ha cesado el fuego. Me temo que van a utilizar "
"observadores para localizar nuestras posiciones y después bombardearlas."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/09"
msgid "The enemy is intensifying the assault toward the west!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo está intensificando el asalto por el oeste!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/10"
msgid "Attention! Enemy aircraft inbound!"
msgstr "¡Atención! ¡Avión enemigo aproximándose!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"Fallschirmjäger! You are doing an excellent job in containing the enemy, but "
"we are struggling to keep up with this massive assault! "
msgstr ""
"¡Fallschirmjäger! Estáis haciendo un excelente trabajo conteniendo al "
"enemigo, ¡pero estamos teniendo problemas para contener este asalto masivo! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"Now that the enemy is giving us some breathing space, I'm ordering you to "
"fall back to our HQ on the other side of the valley. The motorised "
"Kampfgruppe should arrive soon to strengthen our lines there."
msgstr ""
"Ahora que el enemigo nos da un respiro, te ordeno que retrocedas hacia "
"nuestro cuartel general al otro lado del valle. El Kampfgruppe motorizado "
"debería llegar en cualquier momento para reforzar la defensa de esa zona."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/13"
msgid "Our reinforcements are finally here! "
msgstr "¡Por fin han llegado nuestros refuerzos! "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/14"
msgid ""
"Additional reserves, as well as artillery strikes, have been made available "
"to you to make sure the enemy does not take Hill 192."
msgstr ""
"Se han puesto a su disposición reservas adicionales, así como ataques de "
"artillería, para que se asegure de que el enemigo no toma la Colina 192."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/15"
msgid ""
"The enemy will try to attack Hill 192 with everything they've got. But this "
"time, the terrain is our advantage; we hold the high ground. They shouldn't "
"even be trying, but these Americans are tenacious as hell!"
msgstr ""
"El enemigo intentará atacar la Colina 192 con todo lo que tiene. Pero esta "
"vez, la geografía está de nuestra parte; estamos en terreno elevado. Ni "
"siquiera deberían intentarlo, ¡pero estos americanos son tercos como el "
"demonio!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/16"
msgid "Watch out! Americans have managed to flank us on the east!"
msgstr "¡Cuidado! ¡Los americanos han conseguido flanquearnos por el este!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/17"
msgid ""
"A brilliantly executed defense, Fallschirmjäger! The Americans will learn to "
"fear you, Green Devils. At this pace, we will soon push them back into the "
"sea!"
msgstr ""
"¡Una defensa perfectamente ejecutada, Fallschirmjäger! Los americanos "
"aprenderán a temeros, Diablos Verdes. ¡A este ritmo, pronto los mandaremos "
"de vuelta al mar!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/18"
msgid ""
"The Americans have brought their mobile artillery forward. They will likely "
"try to hit the HQ. Avoid placing your troops around the courtyard, and take "
"the artillery out if you can afford to send a detachment right now."
msgstr ""
"Los americanos han adelantado su artillería móvil. Es probable que intenten "
"atacar el cuartel general. Evita colocar tus tropas alrededor del patio, y "
"elimina la artillería si puedes permitirte enviar un destacamento ahora "
"mismo."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/19"
msgid ""
"A fine display of tactical mastery, taking those artillery pieces out! This "
"is why they call on the Fallschirmjäger; to get the job done!"
msgstr ""
"¡Vaya muestra de maestría táctica, derribando esas piezas de artillería! Por "
"eso llaman a los Fallschirmjäger: ¡para acabar el trabajo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/arty"
msgid "Enemy artillery inbound! Keep your heads down, Fallschirmjäger!"
msgstr "¡Se acerca la artillería enemiga! ¡Agachaos, Fallschirmjäger!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/arty2"
msgid ""
"Here comes the American artillery again! The Americans really want to "
"flatten these hedgerows! Take cover!"
msgstr ""
"¡Aquí viene la artillería americana otra vez! ¡Los americanos realmente "
"quieren aplastar este campo! ¡Cúbranse!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/fail_lastwarning"
msgid ""
"The Americans are still inside the perimeter of the HQ! This is your last "
"warning! Have them removed or die trying!"
msgstr ""
"¡Los americanos siguen dentro del perímetro del Cuartel General! ¡Esta es "
"vuestra última advertencia! ¡Eliminadlos o morid en el intento!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/fail_warning"
msgid ""
"Attention! The Americans are inside the HQ perimeter! I want you to take "
"them out within 2 minutes!"
msgstr ""
"¡Atención! ¡Los americanos están dentro del perímetro del Cuartel General! "
"¡Quiero que los eliminen en 2 minutos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/narrator/pzfaust"
msgid ""
"We are very low on AT weaponry, but around the foxholes we have crates with "
"Panzerfausts and other useful tools."
msgstr ""
"Tenemos muy poco armamento AT, pero alrededor de las trincheras tenemos "
"cajas con Panzerfausts y más armamento."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Excellent work! The enemy has been taught a lesson in adaptability and "
"improvisation. Well done, we will be able to contain the Americans in the "
"beachhead. General Schimpf will be very happy to hear about this. "
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo! El enemigo ha recibido una lección de adaptación e "
"improvisación. Bien hecho, seremos capaces de contener a los americanos en "
"la cabeza de playa. El general Schimpf se alegrará mucho de saberlo. "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"We have failed to hold these hills, and the allies can now walk right into "
"St. Lo! Even though you were facing a very strong enemy, General Schimpf "
"will probably not like the news very much. The Fallschirmjäger are not used "
"to losing battles!"
msgstr ""
"Hemos fallado defendiendo estas colinas, ¡y los aliados ahora pueden avanzar "
"directamente hacia St. Lo! Aunque te enfrentabas a un enemigo muy fuerte, al "
"General Schimpf no le va a gustar la noticia. ¡Los Fallschirmjäger "
"acostumbran a perder batallas!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/place"
msgid "3rd Fallschirmjäger Division "
msgstr "3ª División Fallschirmjäger "

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/reinf_arty"
msgid "SfH 18 Artillery Barrage"
msgstr "SfH 18 Andanada de artillería"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/reinf_squad"
msgid "Fallschirmjäger"
msgstr "Fallschirmjäger"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/reinf_squad_ammo"
msgid "Ammo crate"
msgstr "Caja de munición"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/reinf_squad_defensive"
msgid "Fallschirmjäger Recon"
msgstr "Fallschirmjäger de Reconocimiento"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/reinf_squad_irregular"
msgid "Fallschirmjäger Pioniere"
msgstr "Fallschirmjäger Paracaidistas"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/reinf_squad_medic"
msgid "Medic"
msgstr "Médico"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/skip"
msgid "Skip preparation phase"
msgstr "Saltar la fase de preparación"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/story"
msgid " June 10th, 1944. “Festung Europa” is under attack. The allied foothold has expanded in the past 4 days, and now the hills around St. Lô are in the front line. The line north of St. Lô must be held at all costs. Your 3rd Fallschirmjäger Division is setting up positions on the hills in front of St. Lô. The hills are perfect for defense; however, we can’t defend the entire region with the available manpower. The enemy is approaching from the north. Our best bet is to dig in at St. Georges d’Elle.\n\n Set up your line making sure the enemy is being funneled into your killing zones and make sure you defend your AT guns against flanking moves by enemy infantry. Reinforcements are on the way, but they will take some time to get here - if they get here at all. Now, it’s time for your baptism of fire.\n\nHals- und Beinbruch!"
msgstr ""
"10 de junio, 1944.\n"
"\n"
"\"Festung Europa\" está bajo ataque enemigo.\n"
"\n"
"La posición aliada se ha expandido en los últimos 4 días,\n"
"\n"
"y ahora las colinas alrededor de St. Lô están en primera línea.\n"
"\n"
"La línea al norte de St. Lô debe defenderse a toda costa.\n"
"\n"
"Tu 3ª División Fallschirmjäger está estableciendo posiciones\n"
"\n"
"en las colinas frente a St. Lô.\n"
"\n"
"Las colinas son perfectas para la defensa; sin embargo, no podemos\n"
"\n"
"defender toda la región con la cantidad de efectivos disponible.\n"
"\n"
"El enemigo se aproxima por el norte.\n"
"\n"
"Nuestra mejor opción es atrincherarnos en St. Georges d'Elle.\n"
"\n"
"Establezcan su línea asegurándose de que el enemigo sea conducido\n"
"\n"
"hacia las emboscadas y asegúrese de defender sus\n"
"\n"
"cañones AT contra los flanqueos de la infantería enemiga.\n"
"\n"
"Los refuerzos están en camino, pero tardarán en llegar,\n"
"\n"
"si es que llegan.\n"
"\n"
"Ahora, es el momento de vuestro bautismo de fuego.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Hals- und Beinbruch!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/task1"
msgid "Fortify the defensive line at St-Georges d’Elle."
msgstr "Fortificar la línea defensiva en St-Georges d'Elle."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/task2"
msgid "Hold back the Americans and prevent them from breaching the road."
msgstr "Retener a los americanos y evitar que tomen la carretera."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/task3"
msgid "Defend the HQ, prevent the Americans from taking the hill."
msgstr ""
"Defender el Cuartel General, evitar que los americanos tomen la colina."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/task_opt1"
msgid "Send a detachment to eliminate the artillery."
msgstr "Enviar un destacamento para eliminar la artillería."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/timer1"
msgid "Prepare for the American attack!"
msgstr "¡Prepárense para el ataque americano!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/timer2"
msgid "Next American assault in:"
msgstr "Siguiente asalto americano en:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_06_saint_lo_hills/timer3"
msgid ""
"Fall back to the HQ and await reinforcements. Time until our reinforcements "
"arrive:"
msgstr ""
"Retírense al Cuartel General y esperen refuerzos. Tiempo hasta que lleguen "
"los refuerzos:"
